The '''Days of Swiss Linguistics''' (DSL) ([[German language|German]]: Tage der Schweizer Linguistik (TSL), [[French language|French]]: Journées de la linguistique suisses (JLS), [[Italian language|Italian]]: Giornate della linguistica svizzere (GLS)) is a series of linguistics conferences held biennially at one of the [[List of universities in Switzerland|Swiss universities]] on behalf of the [[Swiss Linguistics Society]] (SSG). It is an international conference for researchers from [[Switzerland]], [[Europe]] and beyond. So far, 9 editions of the conference have been carried out.
